            <thetext>IOS mobile safari is very lazy on applying of CSS rules if a big count of DOM elements was rendered.

So I recommended to pre generate all decorator CSS rules on app start up.
This will have an effect like a static CSS file and because of very less DOM elements are rendered, the generation won&#39;t cost much time.</thetext>
